title: JetBrains IntelliJ IDEA 14.0 Ultimate
description:
Year / Date of Release : 2014 
Version : 14.0 Build 139.224 
Developer : JetBrains 
URL: https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/ 
Bit : 32bit, 64bit 
Language : English 
Keygen : Present ( JAR-keygen ) 

System Requirements : 
Microsoft Windows 8.1/8/7/Vista/2003/XP (incl.64-bit)
1 GB RAM minimum, 2 GB RAM recommended
300 MB hard disk space + at least 1GB for caches
1024x768 minimum screen resolution
JDK 1.6 or higher

Description : 
JetBrains IntelliJ IDEA - is a leader among the rapid development in Java. IntelliJ IDEA is a high-tech complex, tightly integrated programming tools, including intelligent Source Editor with advanced automation, powerful refactoring, native support for technologies J2EE, mechanisms of integration test environment Ant / JUnit and version control systems, a unique tool to optimize and test the code Code Inspection, as well as an innovative visual designer graphical interfaces. The unique capabilities of JetBrains IntelliJ IDEA relieve the programmer from the burden of routine work and help in a timely manner to eliminate errors and improve code quality, raising developer productivity to new heights
